{
  "stem": "18281.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we sat maybe third car in line when the British dive bombers attacked that train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I came down from my crate pretty fast and went into the ditch with the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were running just the same.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went into the ditch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were a lot of people killed on the train that morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It probably was only a civilian train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But before the D-day, the Britishes attacked anything that moved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They bombed anything that moved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Any train, any transport was, was attacked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that day, I escaped narrowly again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I told you about Indiana Jones of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I wrote my own uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I believe that when I was stuck at that railroad crossing, I had visited my uncle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That must have been very, very close to D-Day, June 6th, 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had visited him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew that my sister was still in the convent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The rest-- I believed that my parents would come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All through the war, I believed that they were in Holland and they would be back, liberated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we did not know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew in the occupied countries what the Germans did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I certainly didn't have any knowledge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no contact with any outsiders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the, the last farm was the biggest farm where I was, where I I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that-- that was a good farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason it was a good farm, I had a companion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was another boy, again, a fellow from [INAUDIBLE], I think, that was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, I know the location of that farm, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was right near [INAUDIBLE], on the outskirts of [INAUDIBLE] and near the French border.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
